Arvin Industries Inc said raising 150 mln dlrs offering 8-3/8 pct 10-year note 9-1/8 pct 30-year sinking fund debenture .
Lead underwriter offering , 75 mln dlrs , Merrill Lynch Capital Markets .
The note priced 99.63 pct yield 8.43 pct , debenture priced 99.54 pct yield 9.17 pct .
The note redeemable par Arvin 's option March 1 , 1994 .
The debenture redeemable time non-refundable March 1 , 1997 .
Both rated BAA-2 Moody 's Investors Service BBB Standard Poor 's .
